# Umbrella .gitignore for the monmix workspace. Each sub-project keeps its
# own .gitignore for project-specific rules (esp_ui/.gitignore covers the
# IDF build, secrets, dev-loop scratch, etc.); this file only handles
# umbrella-level concerns.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Upstream clones — kept locally as references, NOT vendored.
# Re-clone from upstream rather than pulling into this repo (size + license
# clarity). The slave build flow expects esp-hosted-mcu/ to be a working
# clone of github.com/espressif/esp-hosted-mcu, and case/preview_assembly.scad
# references elecrow-ref/ as a working clone of the CrowPanel reference repo.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/elecrow-ref/
/esp-hosted-mcu/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Runtime state, snapshots, scratch files at the umbrella root.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/pc_sim_state/
/host_performs_slave_ota.zip
/rename_popup.bmp

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Agent-tool scratch directories at any level.
# .copilot — GitHub Copilot CLI session/state
# .claude  — Anthropic Claude Code session/state
# .scratch — ad-hoc working dirs (jar dumps, protobuf research, etc.)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
.copilot/
.claude/
.scratch/

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Generic build / dependency artefacts emitted by any sub-project.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
build/
managed_components/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# One-off reproducer scripts: convention is repro_*.py is local-only.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
repro_*.py
